data.description: Nestled on a desirable cul-de-sac lot, this Energy-Efficient Solar Home is waiting for you! Solar Loan not lease, once the loan is paid in full, you will OWN the system. The perfectly flowing open layout boasts vaulted ceilings, a soothing palette, & tasteful tile and wood flooring throughout. The bright & airy living room showcases media niches & a fireplace, creating a warm & inviting ambiance. The impeccable kitchen is equipped w/white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, & a breakfast bar for quick snacks. The cozy main suite serves as a perfect sanctuary, featuring an ensuite with dual sinks & a walk-in closet. Imagine hosting BBQ cookouts in the lovely backyard, complete with a relaxing covered patio, BBQ grill, water fountain & an outdoor fireplace to gather around on chilly evenings. Make this gem yours!
